  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Puzzle Mania features a numbers crossword puzzle game and assorted variants (Crossword Number Place, Skeleton Crossword & Number Crossword) which requires logic and quick thinking. Ply your guile on a 9x9 tiled board. The game features a complete tutorial in Japanese.\n\nBased on the basic concepts of \"simple and easy to play\", \"deep and addictive\", and \"very exhilarating when the mystery is solved\" - includes 3 types of puzzle games.",
